reen-100 text-green-700 rounded-full font-medium\">О“ВЎГү {preferredCount} в•һВ»u tiв”ңВ¬n</span>\r\n            {blacklistCount > 0 && <span className=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-red-100 text-red-700 rounded-full font-medium\">вүЎЖ’ГңВҪ {blacklistCount} Blacklist</span>}\r\n            {bestGarage && <span className=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 rounded-full font-medium\">вүЎЖ’Г‘Г§ {bestGarage.name} ({parseFloat(bestGarage.avg_rating).toFixed(1)}О“ВЎГү)</span>}\r\n          </div>\r\n        )}\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <input value={search} onChange={e => setSearch(e.target.value)} placeholder=\"Tв”ңВјm garage theo tв”ңВ¬n, в”ҖГҰГҹв•—ГҜa chГҹв•—Г«...\"\r\n        className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-500 focus:border-brand-500 outline-none\" />\r\n\r\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\r\n        {loading ? <p className=\"text-gray-400 col-span-3 text-center py-8\">в”ҖГүang tГҹв•‘Гәi...</p> :\r\n          filtered.length === 0 ? <p className=\"text-gray-400 col-span-3 text-center py-8\">Khв”ңв”Өng cв”ңв”Ӯ garage</p> :\r\n          filtered.map(g => (\r\n            <div key={g.id} className=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border p-4 space-y-3\">\r\n              <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\r\n                <div>\r\n                  <h3 className=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">{g.name}</h3>\r\n                  <p className=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">{g.address}</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div className=\"flex gap-1\">\r\n                  {g.is_preferred && <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-700\">в•һВ»u tiв”ңВ¬n</span>}\r\n                  {g.is_blacklisted && <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700\">Blacklist</span>}\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 