o.available_limit)}</strong>\r\n                          {' '}(vв•һв–‘Гҹв•—Гәt {formatVND(totalAmount - creditInfo.available_limit)})\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        <p className=\"mt-1\">О“ГҘГҶ в”ҖГүв•һГӯn sГҹв•‘в•ң chuyГҹв•—Гўn vГҹв•—Гј trГҹв•‘Гӯng thв”ңГӯi <strong className=\"text-orange-700\">\"ChГҹв•—ВҘ duyГҹв•—Г§t\"</strong> О“ГҮГ¶ cГҹв•‘Вәn quГҹв•‘Гәn lв”ңв•ң/kГҹв•‘в”җ toв”ңГӯn phв”ңВ¬ duyГҹв•—Г§t.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    ) : (\r\n                      <p className=\"text-sm text-green-600 mt-1\">\r\n                        TiГҹв•—Гјn hв”ңГЎng {formatVND(totalAmount)} trong hГҹв•‘Гӯn mГҹв•—вҢҗc khГҹв•‘Гә dГҹв•—Г‘ng {formatVND(creditInfo.available_limit)} О“ГҘГҶ в”ҖГүв•һГӯn sГҹв•‘в•ң <strong>\"в”ҖГүв”ңГә xв”ңГӯc nhГҹв•‘ВЎn\"</strong> О“ВЈГҙ\r\n                      </p>\r\n                    )}\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              )}\r\n\r\n              {creditInfo && totalAmount > 0 && !hasAtpIssue && (\r\n                <div className={`flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg ${\r\n                  creditExceeded ? 'bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200' : 'bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200'\r\n                }`}>\r\n                  <span className=\"text-xl\">вүЎЖ’ГҙГҜ</span>\r\n                  <p className=\"text-sm font-medium\">\r\n                    DГҹв•—в–’ kiГҹв•‘в”җn trГҹв•‘Гӯng thв”ңГӯi в”ҖГҰв•һГӯn sau khi lв•һв–‘u:{' '}\r\n                    <span className={`inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold ${\r\n                      creditExceeded ? 'bg-orange-200 text-orange-800' : 'bg-green-200 text-green-800'\r\n                    }`}>\r\n                      {creditExceeded ? 'О“Г…в”Ӯ ChГҹв•—ВҘ duyГҹв•—Г§t (pending_approval)' : 'О“ВЈГ  в”ҖГүв”ңГә xв”ңГӯc nhГҹв•‘ВЎn (confirmed)'}\r\n                    </span>\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              )}\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        )}\r\n\r\n        {error && <div className=\"bg-red-50 text-red-600 text-sm px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-red-200\">О“ВҘГ® {error}</div>}\r\n\r\n        <div className=\"flex gap-3 items-center\">\r\n          <button type=\"submit\" disabled={submitting || items.length === 0 || hasAtpIssue}\r\n            className=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-600 transition disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\">\r\n            {submitting ? 'в”ҖГүang lв•һв–‘u...' : hasAtpIssue ? 'вүЎЖ’ГңВҪ Khв”ңв”Өng в”ҖГҰГҹв•—Вә tГҹв•—Гҙn kho' : 'вүЎЖ’ГҶв•ӣ Lв•һв–‘u thay в”ҖГҰГҹв•—ГІi'}\r\n          </button>\r\n          <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => router.back()} className=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 transition\">HГҹв•—Вәy</button>\r\n          {hasAtpIssue && (\r\n            <span className=\"text-sm text-red-600 font-medium\">Vui lв”ңв–“ng в”ҖГҰiГҹв•—Гјu chГҹв•—Г«nh sГҹв•—ГҰ lв•һв–‘Гҹв•—Гәng в”ҖГҰГҹв•—Гў lв•һв–‘u в”ҖГҰв•һГӯn</span>\r\n          )}\r\n        </div>\r\n      </form>\r\n    </div>\r\n  )\r\n}\r\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\Beer HL\\bhl-oms\\web\\src\\app\\dashboard\\orders\\[id]\\page.tsx","messages":[{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":2,"message":"'statusLabels' is assigned a value but never used.","line":36,"column":7,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":36,"endColumn":19},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":2,"message":"'statusColors' is assigned a value but never used.","line":37,"column":7,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":37,"endColumn":19},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any","severity":1,"message":"Unexpected any. Specify a different type.","line":51,"column":14,"nodeType":"TSAnyKeyword","messageId":"unexpectedAny","endLine":51,"endColumn":17,"suggestions":[{"messageId":"suggestUnknown","fix":{"range":[2261,2264],"text":"unknown"},"desc":"Use `unknown` instead, thi